---
title: date_to_long_string
description: Convert a date to long format. Same with Jekyll date_to_long_string filter.
version: 10.13.0
works: false
---
<h3>Example 1</h3>
<p>input:
<pre><code>{% raw %}{{ site.time | date_to_long_string }}{% endraw %}</code></pre>
</p>
<p>output:
<pre><code>07 November 2008</code></pre>
</p>
<h3>Example 2</h3>
<p>input:
<pre><code>{% raw %}{{ site.time | date_to_long_string: "ordinal" }}{% endraw %}</code></pre>
</p>
<p>output:
<pre><code>7th November 2008</code></pre>
</p>